channel.title: Omg i gawt dis uder ideuh
channel.description:
Yea, the follow up on "omg i geted uh idueh"
Now that I see people are very interested in my little gimic, I'd like to know who wants to be involved. In case you didn't catch the other thread, I'm going to send a notebook to people on the forums, who will sign in and continue to send it around the world.
First of all, if you haven't registered on the MITB Frappr Map, do so now by clicking here.
Lol fake link, no actually [url=http://www.frappr.com/moparisthebest]here[/url].
State if you can participate and if your willing to pay the money to ship it to the next person.
As a temporary, I'll be the person to get it at the end, or Moparisthebest. Once I get it a poll will be held of who gets it or what happens to it. This may change while it's actually in transaction.
